Class:        Insecta
Habitat:      Meadows
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     0.25 years
Weight:       0.0005 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Migrates 4,800 km; uses Earth's magnetic field for navigation

Name:         Axolotl
Scientific:   Ambystoma mexicanum
Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

Name:         Komodo Dragon
